{"tid":2279268,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【港講文學】深夜時分，陪你看捷克詩人Miroslav Holub的詩歌","createTime":"2020-11-09T16:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T17:59:50.000Z","uid":17335,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72ea844da4b91da938639507ba36b04cab37de6a","tid":2279268,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><p class=\"center\">勁過魯迅？捷克詩人從醫也從文</p><br />\n<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2020/9/zg7waqhb3cdzep77g92kby52xkvwry.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2020%2F9%2Fzg7waqhb3cdzep77g92kby52xkvwry.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=2e8e517c&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n好多名人傳記，都講到他們曾經讀醫，亦因為不同原因，放棄行醫，成功轉行。例如，大家耳熟能詳的魯迅從文、孫中山從政等。難怪香港狀元總愛讀醫，果然有助擔任社會賢達。<br />\n<br />\n話說近年相當有Guts主動訪台，參議院院長演講「我是一個台灣人」，當今之世敢向強國Say no的捷克，亦出過一個「從醫又從文」的作家。<br />\n<br />\n米羅斯拉夫&middot;霍爾布（Miroslav Holub），既是免疫學家，亦寫下不少出色的詩，其詩集之名都符合他的身份和工作，《深切治療》（Intensive Care）。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ARE4wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ARE4wD.png&h=ccbc812b&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n平行綜合症 <br />\n米羅斯拉夫&middot;霍爾布／石刻一熊譯<br />\n<br />\n由我們自己去畫的話<br />\n兩條平行線<br />\n總會相遇。<br />\n<br />\n問題在於<br />\n是在前頭<br />\n抑或在我們身後。<br />\n<br />\n遠方的火車到底<br />\n迎面前來<br />\n或是正在離開。<br />\n<br />\n或許你和我都試過，就算有一把尺幫手，但當我們將線不停延長，最後一對平行線始終都無法保持平行。如果將平行線一路用人手延長未來在前面，或者後面，兩條線總會在遠方互相交接。<br />\n<br />\n詩人從平行線的延展，聯想到火車，平行線的長短。或者線還可以由自己去繪畫，但是火車的行駛，那有如機械式決定的命運，我們就控制不了。<br />\n<br />\n手繪平行線和火車軌的不同在於，線縱可延伸，始終難以保持平衡；火車鐵軌雖然平衡，乘客卻無法永遠與之並行、掌控。<br />\n<br />\n看到這裡，大家有否感受到，詩中有份不安與躊躇的失落呢？即使命定般的相遇，卻無法掌握時機，是遲來，抑或早到，總是不由自主。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545414687-4ab460a92371?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&amp;ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;q=60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1545414687-4ab460a92371%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.2.1%26ixid%3DeyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D800%26q%3D60&h=d67e4f40&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n如果你有其他睇法，歡迎分享。最後大家還想看我，石刻一熊，翻譯、介紹更多精彩外國文學，記得CLS（comment, like and share）！"},{"pid":"847490534ec5897de76d9d21cf206297e4f0a29b","tid":2279268,"uid":17335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ds80vk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ds80vk.jpg&h=76faf9de&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n想睇更多文藝嘢，歡迎Follow德尼思化：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdelis.ver%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9yzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=a4d16c25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDelisver.hk%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9yzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=83b2bc0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/</a><br />\nMedium <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36HvepQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36HvepQ&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9yzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=9aa93889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36HvepQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065711546cba7d6b328aa3c47b5820a412b0129a","tid":2279268,"uid":245711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,